<chapter version="5.0" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
				 xml:lang="en">

	<title>Discovering NovaForgeTM</title>

	<sect2>
		<title>Authentication</title>

		<para>To use the forge, identify yourself by entering your login and
			password.</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Authentication</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-00-login.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>

	<sect2>
		<title>Navigation</title>

		<para>Novaforge allows navigation on 3 levels: left menu, tabs
			(projects) and sub-tabs (applications).</para>

		<para>The content is always displayed in the central area.</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Content</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-01-intro.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>

	<sect2>
		<title>Projects menu</title>

		<para>Each tab represents an open project. To navigate, click a tab.
		</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Projects tabs</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-015-ongletsProjets.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>

	<sect2>
		<title>Left menu</title>

		<para>The left menu contains the drop-down list of available
			applications. To open an application, click its name.</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Left menu</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-02-menuGauche.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>

	<sect2>
		<title>Applications</title>

		<para>With the Novaforge interface, several tabs (applications) can be
			open at the same time. To navigate, click a tab.</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Applications tab</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-03-menuHaut.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>


	<sect2>
		<title>Projects quick menu</title>

		<para>You can change project at any time. The projects menu lists all
			available projects.</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Projects quick menu</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-04-menuProjets.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>

	<sect2>
		<title>Account menu</title>

		<para>Use the account menu to access the account parameters and online
			help and to log off.</para>

		<figure>
			<title>Account menu</title>

			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="02-05-menuCompte.png"
						width="450px" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</figure>


	</sect2>
</chapter>

